des:
Ask Liquor Emporium for any coupons or deals. For example you can
- ask "liquor emporium for the deal of the day" or 
- ask "liquor emporium find me some coupons" or
- ask "liquor emporium for any deals" or 
- ask "liquor emporium for any coupons"
- ask "help"
